nodes.text: The Musical Rocks, known as Queee-ha in Gacerian, were a collection of boulders on the Plateau of Dreams, located on the Elto continent of the planet Gacerian. As the wind blew through the boulders, it produced eerie musics. Gacerites mediated at the Musical Rocks, and it was the closest place the Gacerites had to a religious shrine.
